{"title":"nginx配置不生效","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.021Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/nginx配置不生效","updated":"2023-07-28T09:19:57.759Z","content":"<p>1、先确认是否存在多个nginx配置文件以及配置是否正确</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">nginx <span class=\"literal\">-t</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/5a75fde5e4e54138b555c4ab58079149.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n可以看到我这里反馈出/etc/nginx/nginx.conf的配置文件配置正常。</p>\n<p>如果你这里出现的配置文件路径与你配置的不符合，关闭nginx服务，并指定配置文件路径启动。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#关闭nginx</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">nginx <span class=\"literal\">-s</span> stop</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#使用指定的配置文件启动nginx</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">nginx <span class=\"literal\">-c</span> <span class=\"variable\">$</span>&#123;你的配置文件路径&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#例如</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#nginx -c /etc/nginx/nginx.conf</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>2、如果上述检查无误，确认nginx中是否包含了默认配置文件<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/962d6b92256d4cd7ba56c0f799d8abb3.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n可以尝试将上面两行配置注释掉。<br>\n然后<code>nginx -s reload</code>重启一下服务再试一下。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"mysql连接失败error msg_Failed to start connection pool -- SSL connection error_ protocol version mismatc","link":"2023/07/28/mysql连接失败error msg_Failed to start connection pool -- SSL connection error_ protocol version mismatc"},"next":{"title":"Maven环境的安装","link":"2023/07/28/Maven环境的安装"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/nginx配置不生效/","reading_time":"214 字约 1 分钟"}